"
inoremap <silent> <Plug>(vsnip-jump-next) <Esc>:<C-u>call <SID>jump(1)<CR>
snoremap <silent> <Plug>(vsnip-jump-next) <Esc>:<C-u>call <SID>jump(1)<CR>
inoremap <silent> <Plug>(vsnip-jump-prev) <Esc>:<C-u>call <SID>jump(-1)<CR>
